1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,500
Hello.

2
00:00:02,500 --> 00:00:05,500
I'm Yeon Sam-heum, a solo developer.

3
00:00:05,500 --> 00:00:08,500
Over 17 years of running my company,

4
00:00:08,500 --> 00:00:14,000
I've built over 200 websites and
600,000 pages together with AI.

5
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:17,000
This submission is not something I built from scratch.

6
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:20,000
It grew over 8 years — WIA Geulsalim.

7
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:26,000
95% of humanity's 5,000 years of knowledge
is still out of reach.

8
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:32,000
87% of Korean historical documents
remain undigitized, quietly decaying.

9
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:40,000
Of the world's 7,000 languages, 97% have
severely inadequate or no AI translation and voice support.

10
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:45,000
300 million people with sensory disabilities
still cannot access written text.

11
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:50,000
These four barriers must be broken at once.

12
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:54,500
Geulsalim is a 4-stage pipeline —
Restore · Structure · Convert · Deliver.

13
00:00:54,500 --> 00:00:59,500
Let me show you directly
through four live demos.

14
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:04,000
Demo 1 — Restoration.

15
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:10,000
A Diffusion model restores damaged historical documents,
while an LLM infers missing characters.

16
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:14,000
Restoration is not manipulation.

17
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:20,000
The original hash is permanently preserved.

18
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:29,000
Demo 2 — Structuring.

19
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:36,000
Untagged PDFs are automatically converted to
WCAG 2.2-compliant HTML with AI-generated alt text.

20
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:42,000
At our WIA Book accessibility checker,
I already run 80 automated audit items.

21
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:54,000
Demo 3 — EPUB Accessibility Restoration.

22
00:01:54,000 --> 00:02:00,000
Non-compliant EPUB 2 files are
automatically restored to EPUB 3.

23
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:06,000
Passing all 80 accessibility audit items.

24
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:13,000
WCAG, EPUB A11y, KS X 6201, EU EAA —
satisfying four international standards simultaneously.

25
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:19,000
Demo 4 — Multimodal Delivery.

26
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:24,000
Braille in 7,000 languages,
voice in 254 languages,

27
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:29,000
WIA Talk 3D sign language,
436 interactive tools and simulators.

28
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:36,000
WIA Live — where Deaf and visually impaired users
communicate directly without interpreters.

29
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:39,500
Already in pilot operation.

30
00:02:40,500 --> 00:02:43,000
We're Geulsalim.

31
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:46,000
Hongik Ingan — Benefit all widely,
sustainably. We're Geulsalim.
